{"tid":2295212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話時話，你哋有無睇過呢個game?","createTime":"2020-11-21T15:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T11:50:47.000Z","uid":132888,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39755121c7d5dc8090f02c9bc20520817d6b8c78","tid":2295212,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"Hello大家好，我哋最近構思咗一副以「貓城抗爭」為題材嘅Boardgame--《無名貓:黎明之戰》，仲放左上Kickstarter眾籌，如果成功嘅就可以進入生產階段，依家只係淨返4日就到deadline，所以希望大家可以支持我哋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/freedomsoulsgame/371192491?ref=project_build\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Ffreedomsoulsgame%2F371192491%3Fref%3Dproject_build&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5f6679f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/freedomsoulsgame/371192491?ref=project_build</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VKUiar.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VKUiar.png&h=12df1540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋上個星期都有出過個post：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2283361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2283361/page/1</a><br />\n咁今日我哋想講多多啲有關個Boardgame嘅內容!<br />\n<br />\n&quot;《無名貓：黎明之戰》是一個2-5人的遊戲，你們將會扮演覺醒了的貓去對抗各個邪惡主腦。在遊戲中你可以去攻擊敵人、移動到不同區域、偵察敵人和搜尋物品，互相配合以完成不同的任務。而當所有玩家完成各自的回合,便輪到主腦的邪惡行動...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n係呢個game入面大家可以選擇飾演唔同嘅角色：例如老伯、急救、記者，甚至一啲好普通嘅人。雖然佢哋入面有好多都係好平凡嘅人，但佢哋選擇咗去做佢哋能力所及嘅事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPoqpQu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPoqpQu.jpg&h=f7f50efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲進行時，你哋可以用每個玩家都有嘅基本卡; 每個角色都唔同嘅角色專屬卡; 加上可以利用搜索搵到嘅物品卡，去同敵人戰鬥!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnSFYax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnSFYax.jpg&h=637a8416&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cM9MTJU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcM9MTJU.png&h=50e7ed95&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R94tnCg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR94tnCg.png&h=c561da98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係遊戲開始前，你可以選擇唔同嘅「主腦」去做整局遊戲嘅敵人。<br />\n當然，敵人一定唔會得一個，每個主腦都會有佢哋獨有嘅牌組，入面會有唔同嘅爪牙、裝備同埋詭謀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x0TRkoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0TRkoZ.jpg&h=fa65afee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJp5pQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJp5pQF.png&h=a66ad762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上就係《無名貓:黎明之戰》嘅大致遊戲形式，如果大家想知多啲嘅話，可以入去上面Kickstarter嘅link，或者去我哋嘅社交網站都可以搵到多啲嘅資訊。<br />\nKickstarter: <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/freedomsoulsgame/371192491?ref=project_build\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Ffreedomsoulsgame%2F371192491%3Fref%3Dproject_build&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5f6679f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/freedomsoulsgame/371192491?ref=project_build</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/freedomsoulsgame/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffreedomsoulsgame%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=88c1f304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/freedomsoulsgame/</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/freedomsouls3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffreedomsouls3&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b7d74e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/freedomsouls3</a><br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E8%B2%93%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-FreedomSouls-105196828064542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25B2%2593%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2588%25B0-FreedomSouls-105196828064542&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=0684b215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E8%B2%93%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-FreedomSouls-105196828064542</a>"},{"pid":"0ad028fff0bda2343f04d1f3e1be6aafe551db88","tid":2295212,"uid":132888,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"老實講，我哋都唔肯定用呢個題材整呢隻game係「啱」定「錯」。<br />\n<br />\n但我哋都認同有一啲野唔可以攞嚟玩，再多冠冕堂皇嘅藉口都唔可以過界。<br />\n所以係個game入面冇理大，亦冇任何已經離世嘅人。我哋都講唔到一個好清楚嘅界線邊啲可以加入去，邊啲唔可以，都只係我哋一個嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n係個game入面，玩家可以隨時quit game(冇錯，規則上真係可以隨時脫離)，但被留低嘅人可能就會走唔到，就算形勢大好都可能會反轉。(當然，死都唔走，留底戀戰都可能會輸，但呢個又係另一個議題。)<br />\n<br />\n我哋想講嘅係，「齊上齊落」唔係一個口號咁簡單。<br />\n個game入面有個「換裝機制」，每個角色都可以「上/落裝」。冇邊一面係一定勁啲，只係唔同時候有唔同功能，就好似現實咁﹕適當嘅時候做適當嘅事。<br />\n同時亦想講，只要願意，每一個人都可以「換裝」，去做一啲佢哋做到嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我哋唔係想為任何事去做一個結論，我哋只係想透過遊戲去傳遞一啲「信念」，僅此而已。"},{"pid":"4e4ca05552ecf5c2855e2fa2b5c3bc8cf21e90a9","tid":2295212,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd8deed549a578de39325419d83c4e603e07f70","tid":2295212,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"推&times;2<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8833e54acffb514c7fe276a986cc7f12f4118e","tid":2295212,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d374ec35f69843a231e7de8d760afbf0337271d6","tid":2295212,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"推&times;3<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0791e966944f6d70933835bdc05fbdcc6748a14","tid":2295212,"uid":132888,"like"